title: Message for Jack
author: Thousand_Miles
pages:
#- Hey spacejack, 3/12/2012 Thousand_Miles here.
enchanting table, armory broken into, sheep killed in the farm. I would like to get online when you are to discuss what we do. I found a resource chest unlocked but not raided. ill keep it safe till you're on
#- read this I would say where it is. Should I keep it on my person or in a chest somewhere? It's nice that books allow more text than signs. Leave a response book in my place.
#- 